<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lower-vt">lower <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ləʊə(r)/    美 /'loʊər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>把…放低；把…降下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lower a flag 
降旗</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>lowered her eyes</strong>, shaking her head slightly. 
她垂下眼睛，轻轻地摇了摇头。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>降低；减低 (价格、声音等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lower expenses / one’s voice / pressure / blood sugar levels
减少开支/压低嗓门/减轻压力/降低血糖水平</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This shop has lowered its prices. 
这家商店已降低了价格。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lower public health emergency response level
降低公共卫生应急响应级别</p><footer>2020江苏</footer></div></div>